author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
I don't know much about Breaking Benjamin - but I know there was some excitement about "Awaken" when it came out in October - and last week the band released a video to go with it, so I thought I would take a look. It's epic. Sadly, you wouldn't know that I watched all of it because the thinking computer's copyright detector went into overdrive and limited what could be shown. To see the full video, visit here: https://youtu.be/w0GfewGYR3g?si=yhwNE7FnkxJV5rFD

You can watch the full interview with Ben on 93X Radio by visiting here: https://youtu.be/RIgg0TtRvFg?si=PKNTXN_GPAkLQyWE

The new Darkness album comes out in March, you can pre-order 'Dreams On Toast' on CD, vinyl or cassette here: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/
Stream / Download the latest single 'I Hate Myself': https://thedarkness.lnk.to/ihm

The Darkness are also going on tour across the UK in March, tickets are on sale here: https://www.thedarknesslive.com/tour-dates/

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/
